1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,112
Your favorite beach could vanish in a storm.

2
00:00:03,062 --> 00:00:06,512
Every 30 seconds, a shoreline is swallowed.

3
00:00:06,512 --> 00:00:10,550
Storms now double erosion, battering coastlines daily.

4
00:00:10,550 --> 00:00:16,025
Sea levels rise 8mm a year, a new record since 1944.

5
00:00:16,025 --> 00:00:20,012
Sinkholes pop above streets, smashing whole neighborhoods.

6
00:00:20,012 --> 00:00:23,300
The next wave could erase your hometown forever.

7
00:00:23,300 --> 00:00:26,650
Imagine seeing yesterday's landmarks drowned.

8
00:00:26,650 --> 00:00:28,537
Stop scrolling.

9
00:00:28,537 --> 00:00:30,950
This is your sign to level up.

10
00:00:30,950 --> 00:00:32,450
Follow.

11
00:00:32,450 --> 00:00:34,125
What next?

12
00:00:34,125 --> 00:00:37,012
The ice coastlines that keep us cold.

